---
title: Spicy Black Bean Tortilla Stacks with Guacamole and Green-Onion Rice
description: What's better than a quesadilla? A stack of quesadillas sliced into beany wedges of deliciousness! We snuck some extra heat into the Mexican-style spiced rice for a quick kick of flavour!
